---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Accessibility — Sarif Consulting"
  description="Accessibility commitment for Sarif Consulting: WCAG 2.1 AA where feasible, limitations of WebGL and motion, and how to request accommodations."
>
  <section class="policy-hero section" aria-label="Accessibility statement header">
    <div class="container policy-hero-inner">
      <p class="section-label">Commitment</p>
      <h1 class="section-header">Accessibility</h1>
      <p class="policy-meta">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="policy-body section cv-auto" data-cv-size="xxl" aria-label="Accessibility statement content">
    <div class="container policy-content page-reads-over-lobby">
      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">Our commitment</h2>
        <p>
          Sarif Consulting strives to meet <strong>WCAG 2.1 Level AA</strong> for core site content
          (navigation, text, forms and legal pages) where it is reasonably achievable. We treat
          accessibility as an ongoing practice, not a one-time checklist.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">Known limitations</h2>
        <p>
          Parts of this site use <strong>WebGL</strong>, <strong>motion</strong> and optional
          <strong>ambient audio</strong> for an immersive experience. These layers may be difficult
          or impossible to use with some assistive technologies, on low-power devices, or when motion
          is reduced. The audio control in the footer is <strong>off by default</strong> and only
          activates if you opt in; we respect <code>prefers-reduced-motion</code> by hiding the
          ambient-audio toggle when reduced motion is requested.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Core paths</strong> — including contact, services overview, legal policies and
          this statement — are designed to remain usable without relying on the 3D lobby or
          decorative motion.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-heading">Feedback and accommodations</h2>
        <p>
          If you encounter a barrier or need information in a different format, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:info@sarifconsulting.ai" class="policy-link">info@sarifconsulting.ai</a>.
          We will work with you on reasonable accommodations where we can. For how we handle
          personal data when you reach out, see our
          <a href="/privacy/" class="policy-link">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .policy-hero {
    padding-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .policy-hero-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .policy-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    opacity: 0.6;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .policy-body {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .policy-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .policy-section {
    margin-bottom: 52px;
    padding-bottom: 52px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .policy-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .policy-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--cyan-bright);
    text-shadow: var(--cyan-glow-text);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .policy-content p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .policy-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .policy-content code {
    font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    color: var(--chrome-dark);
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08);
    padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .policy-link {
    color: var(--cyan-core);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
    transition: color 0.2s ease, text-decoration-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .policy-link:hover {
    color: var(--cyan-bright);
    text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .policy-link:focus {
    outline: none;
  }

  .policy-link:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--cyan-core);
    outline-offset: 3px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .policy-link {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
